sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Test Case: TC_011_2_CSMS
    Note over CP,CS: Remote Start Charging Session – Time Out

    CS->>CP: 1. RemoteStartTransaction.req (idTag)
    CP-->>CS: 2. RemoteStartTransaction.conf (status=Accepted)
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Accepted

    CP->>CS: 3. Authorize.req (idTag from step 1)
    CS-->>CP: 4. Authorize.conf (idTagInfo.status=Accepted)
    Note over CS: Validation: idTagInfo.status must be Accepted

    CP->>CS: 5. StatusNotification.req (status=Preparing, errorCode=NoError)
    CS-->>CP: 6. StatusNotification.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Preparing

    Note over CP: [Connection timeout reached – cable not plugged in]

    CP->>CS: 7. StatusNotification.req (status=Available, errorCode=NoError)
    CS-->>CP: 8. StatusNotification.conf
    Note over CP: Validation: status must be Available
